    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A zinc-hydroxy compound with chemical formula Zn5(OH)8Cl2 H2O. It is used to coat substrates normally infested by algae, such as concrete roofing tiles and other silicate-containing building materials, to prevent or minimize algal infestation.</Note_Text>
